{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DataInputStreamRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DataInputStreamRef\/InputStreamProtocol-Implementations"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tries to read "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"text":" bytes from the stream into the buffer starting at","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"buffer","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Will block during this read.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"read"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"buffer","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"count","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","text":"CancellableRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize","text":"gssize","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If count is zero returns zero and does nothing. A value of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"larger than "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"G_MAXSSIZE"},{"text":" will cause a ","type":"text"},{"code":"invalidArgument","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" error."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"On success, the number of bytes read into the buffer is returned.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can happen e.g. near the end of a file. Zero is returned on end of file"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(or if "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is zero),  but never otherwise."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The returned "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"text":" is not a nul-terminated string, it can contain nul bytes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"at any position, and this function doesn’t nul-terminate the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"text":" is not ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", then the operation can be cancelled by","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancelled"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned. If an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"partial result will be returned, without an error.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On error -1 is returned and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"type":"text","text":" is set accordingly."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DataInputStreamRef\/read(buffer:count:cancellable:)"},"variants":